---
title: Oven-Baked Chorizo, Chicken & Veggie Risotto with Parmesan & Baby Leaves
description: We believe weeknight dinners should be tasty and on the table without too much fuss. Hence, we present you with our oven-baked chorizo & chicken risotto. Minimal stirring, loads of comforting veggies and superbly satisfying, what could be better?
